{"tid":2048927,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁志祥冀政府為身處內地卻未能回港工作港人提供支援","createTime":"2020-06-03T06:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T07:27:02.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c63234fd4b839b241c37348ecfb54fb396649e21","tid":2048927,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"梁志祥冀政府為身處內地卻未能回港工作港人提供支援<br />\n2020-06-03 HKT 13:14<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員梁志祥說，接獲住在內地但在港工作的人士求助，他們目前未獲隔離令豁免，不能回港工作，因此沒有收入，處於水深火熱狀態，希望政府關注他們的情況，研究用綜援等政策為他們提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n另一名民建聯議員周浩鼎就說，幼稚園將於本月中復課，他接獲跨境學童父母求助，擔心未能安排跨境校巴或保姆車接送需要照料的學童上學，父母亦因為工作原因及隔離令仍然生效，未能送子女跨境上學，希望局方能夠作出適當安排。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529938-20200603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529938-20200603.htm&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=1189ab05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529938-20200603.htm&h=51f132bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529938-20200603.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2ed1d590e9d2ab685fc55c2a5b8042de541e4b76","tid":2048927,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"坐大飛囉"},{"pid":"9715d124f26987034eb3f771685129e83aaf109f","tid":2048927,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"跨境學童咪用緊online teaching"},{"pid":"240ae664e4441c23b8c510d80e3d5660da608f6e","tid":2048927,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9715d124f26987034eb3f771685129e83aaf109f","tid":2048927,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"跨境學童咪用緊online teaching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"online working la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets